{"tid":2190032,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"網民發起明日九龍遊行　警方稱會部署足夠警力果斷執法","createTime":"2020-09-05T10:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T10:13:08.000Z","uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"21721a8bd3ea54017ab39db571db340bb4ac3a54","tid":2190032,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T10:07:14.000Z","msg":"警方表示，就網上有人發起明天在九龍區遊行，警方明日會在西九龍一帶部署足夠警力，其他警區亦會提高戒備，如發現任何涉嫌違法行為，定必立即介入及果斷執法。<br />\n<br />\n警方在社交網站說，昨日已發文提醒公眾，任何人組織或參與相關活動，均有可能觸犯《公安條例》及《預防及控制疾病(禁止羣組聚集)規例》，但有人在網上繼續鼓吹他人參與是次活動，聲言要「重燃戰火」、「絕地反擊」。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，有關活動屬未經批准集結，亦屬受禁羣組聚集，任何人組織或參與，甚至進行暴力衝擊，均屬違法。警方會迅速果斷執法，適時拘捕，絕不手軟。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548028-20200905.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548028-20200905.htm&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmRw%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=448f98df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548028-20200905.htm&h=c4de750b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548028-20200905.htm</a>"},{"pid":"24b2d056c4f40b182d7adafdc4d539a4ff133339","tid":2190032,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T10:09:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"160c09c2136d10eb119756dbe70bfdb68e1001fa","tid":2190032,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24b2d056c4f40b182d7adafdc4d539a4ff133339","tid":2190032,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T10:09:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T10:13:08.000Z","msg":"Post新聞囉 可以有咩居心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}